---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import FeatureCard from '../components/FeatureCard.astro';
---

<Layout title="ChatAndBuild Guide - From Idea to App with Zero Coding Experience">
	<div class="hero">
		<div class="container">
			<h1>Turn Your Ideas Into Reality <span class="text-gradient">Without Writing Code</span></h1>
			<p class="subtitle">A complete beginner's guide to using ChatAndBuild to create apps, websites, and more - even if you've never coded before.</p>
			<div class="cta-buttons">
				<a href="/getting-started" class="btn">Get Started</a>
				<a href="/examples" class="btn btn-secondary">View Examples</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<section class="container">
		<h2>What is <span class="text-gradient">ChatAndBuild</span>?</h2>
		<p>ChatAndBuild is a revolutionary platform that allows anyone to build web applications, websites, and software through simple conversation. No coding experience required! Just describe what you want to build, and the AI will help you create it step by step.</p>
		
		<div class="image-container">
			<img src="/images/chatandbuild-interface.png" alt="ChatAndBuild Interface" />
		</div>
		
		<h2>Why Use ChatAndBuild?</h2>
		<div class="grid">
			<FeatureCard 
				title="No Coding Required" 
				description="Build real applications without writing a single line of code. Just describe what you want in plain English."
				icon="🚀"
			/>
			<FeatureCard 
				title="Learn As You Go" 
				description="Understand the basics of web development while building your project with helpful explanations."
				icon="📚"
			/>
			<FeatureCard 
				title="From Idea to Deployment" 
				description="Complete the entire development process from initial concept to a live, deployed application."
				icon="🌐"
			/>
			<FeatureCard 
				title="Customizable" 
				description="Create exactly what you need with full customization options through simple conversation."
				icon="🎨"
			/>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="container">
		<h2>How It Works</h2>
		<div class="step-container">
			<div class="step">
				<div class="step-number">1</div>
				<div class="step-content">
					<h3>Describe Your Idea</h3>
					<p>Start by telling ChatAndBuild what you want to create. Be as specific as possible about the features and functionality you need. For example: "I want to build a recipe sharing website where users can upload recipes, search by ingredients, and save favorites."</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="step">
				<div class="step-number">2</div>
				<div class="step-content">
					<h3>Refine Through Conversation</h3>
					<p>ChatAndBuild will ask clarifying questions and suggest features. This conversation helps refine your idea and ensures the final product matches your vision. You can request changes, add features, or ask questions at any point.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="step">
				<div class="step-number">3</div>
				<div class="step-content">
					<h3>Watch Your App Take Shape</h3>
					<p>As you converse with ChatAndBuild, it will create the necessary files, code, and structure for your application. You'll see your idea come to life in real-time with a live preview of your application.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="step">
				<div class="step-number">4</div>
				<div class="step-content">
					<h3>Test and Refine</h3>
					<p>Try out your application as it's being built. If something doesn't work as expected or you want to make changes, simply tell ChatAndBuild what needs to be fixed or added.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="step">
				<div class="step-number">5</div>
				<div class="step-content">
					<h3>Deploy Your Creation</h3>
					<p>When you're happy with your application, ChatAndBuild will help you deploy it to the web so others can use it. You'll get a public URL to share with friends, family, or potential users.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="cta-section">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Ready to Build Your First App?</h2>
			<p>Follow our step-by-step guide to create your first application with ChatAndBuild - no coding experience required!</p>
			<a href="/getting-started" class="btn">Get Started Now</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.hero {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(var(--primary-dark), 0.9), rgba(var(--secondary-dark), 0.9)), 
					url('/images/hero-bg.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;
		color: white;
		padding: 4rem 0;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}
	
	.hero h1 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	
	.subtitle {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto 2rem;
		opacity: 0.9;
	}
	
	.cta-buttons {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		justify-content: center;
	}
	
	.cta-section {
		background-color: rgb(var(--primary-dark));
		color: white;
		padding: 4rem 0;
		text-align: center;
		margin-top: 3rem;
	}
	
	.cta-section h2 {
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	
	.cta-section p {
		max-width: 600px;
		margin: 0 auto 2rem;
		opacity: 0.9;
	}
	
	.cta-section .btn {
		background-color: white;
		color: rgb(var(--primary-dark));
	}
	
	.cta-section .btn:hover {
		background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
	}
	
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.hero h1 {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
		}
		
		.cta-buttons {
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: center;
		}
	}
</style>
